{"tid":21694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打有注意力不足過動症ADHD?","createTime":"2016-12-04T04:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T15:24:22.000Z","uid":46265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8609246d423c25c9fed2dab1229a037cbf1e1bda","tid":21694,"uid":46265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:24:46.000Z","msg":"自細都覺得自己做野好唔專心<br />\n番學上堂做功課温書唔在講<br />\n出到黎做野都係咁<br />\n成日做做下task A 個腦就醒起task B 啲野<br />\n跟住就不自覺地去做task B 點知轉頭又諗起task C<br />\n最後三樣野都做到一半半<br />\n連拍拖同女朋友食飯都好易俾隔離枱啲人講野分心<br />\n不能自控地聽人講嘢但個心覺得煩到仆街<br />\n懷疑自己有ADHD<br />\n有冇巴打都係苦主<br />\n想過去醫但好貴唔知值唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dded8654e2b01a65d0fa231e8a249dbba0920bed","tid":21694,"uid":46265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e400a515d9ef0479e51d1acae8277db48041494a","tid":21694,"uid":4128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:31:06.000Z","msg":"我有"},{"pid":"b0379bde4ffd1952ce2c37225e13cb54c2b9591f","tid":21694,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"068b374db00df7ae7368acc6dddd32ddbfd197b9","tid":21694,"uid":46265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有</blockquote><br />\n是不是因為你的ADHD很嚴重<br />\n覆完句我有就去左睇其他post唔講多啲我知??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個病真係好可怕"},{"pid":"82b79dfba6edbe425888b3b44468543e08b10393","tid":21694,"uid":35946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n求link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a5f0f7b1f4fa278ca6e98a197e08b8eae80423","tid":21694,"uid":51573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ADHD 撚在此"},{"pid":"ede1f4dcf69515401512619d93c8fdca5b5a476f","tid":21694,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n求link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.adhd.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.adhd.hk%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6QT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=c6999ce7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.adhd.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"9032b0ce2f081f4deb505cf44c04506ad3c3f853","tid":21694,"uid":46265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:43:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做過幾個網上測驗都話我好大機會有ADHD<br />\n不過我見去搵私家醫生check要成幾千蚊<br />\n想知食完藥效果係咪真係好唔同"},{"pid":"dde1843293f1a7018c0a4bd5ac824559902d4e53","tid":21694,"uid":51573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做過幾個網上測驗都話我好大機會有ADHD<br />\n不過我見去搵私家醫生check要成幾千蚊<br />\n想知食完藥效果係咪真係好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non 9 啦唔撚好信西醫<br />\n自己生活調節返就得<br />\n同正常人一齊生活無問題"},{"pid":"b76d5e8a5377356b6e404a41d3b3a7a142226e2b","tid":21694,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:45:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做過幾個網上測驗都話我好大機會有ADHD<br />\n不過我見去搵私家醫生check要成幾千蚊<br />\n想知食完藥效果係咪真係好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果影響唔大就算啦 <br />\n分分鐘食藥嘅附作用重大"},{"pid":"f2ea641b6e1d2a2bd7145b3ddfb7290ca2084674","tid":21694,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:48:46.000Z","msg":"幾十歲重應唔應該check, 去邊度check <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba8b59772fb695ed7783a3004ab64ce598b2980","tid":21694,"uid":46265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:50:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做過幾個網上測驗都話我好大機會有ADHD<br />\n不過我見去搵私家醫生check要成幾千蚊<br />\n想知食完藥效果係咪真係好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果影響唔大就算啦 <br />\n分分鐘食藥嘅附作用重大</blockquote><br />\n有咩副作用？<br />\n記性變差之類？"},{"pid":"c10772fa440c37e470bbf79cb33ca990053e4254","tid":21694,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做過幾個網上測驗都話我好大機會有ADHD<br />\n不過我見去搵私家醫生check要成幾千蚊<br />\n想知食完藥效果係咪真係好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果影響唔大就算啦 <br />\n分分鐘食藥嘅附作用重大</blockquote><br />\n有咩副作用？<br />\n記性變差之類？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣就唔清楚 <br />\n但點都有啲附作用嘅"},{"pid":"ff3c8dfd4c16a302563b67a9b3eb40cda2a7e6d6","tid":21694,"uid":46265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T06:24:23.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打曾經睇過醫生分享下用藥後感"},{"pid":"a02af2be39725203dc44538a00a1f0f59742d16b","tid":21694,"uid":47869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"比樓主情況更嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇私家醫生介紹"},{"pid":"d8d0e870fcbabbc90afd13573210e79d8c30cc5b","tid":21694,"uid":46265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T23:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd32dd8fb1b02dde7ff4f14911b556fc625d41eb","tid":21694,"uid":25173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T23:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做過幾個網上測驗都話我好大機會有ADHD<br />\n不過我見去搵私家醫生check要成幾千蚊<br />\n想知食完藥效果係咪真係好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non 9 啦唔撚好信西醫<br />\n自己生活調節返就得<br />\n同正常人一齊生活無問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗你試過幾次因為呢樣野鎖左自己出屋<br />\n或者鎖左自己架車 <br />\n你就明唔係你好努力去調節就會好"},{"pid":"f3d9335613aff3524f56fff553aaa526d164d56b","tid":21694,"uid":117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我有</blockquote><br />\n是不是因為你的ADHD很嚴重<br />\n覆完句我有就去左睇其他post唔講多啲我知??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個病真係好可怕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5406a317efc4d56cfc35300be740c13f82b88eb9","tid":21694,"uid":19385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T00:25:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做過幾個網上測驗都話我好大機會有ADHD<br />\n不過我見去搵私家醫生check要成幾千蚊<br />\n想知食完藥效果係咪真係好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nADHD撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拖左好多年都唔想去睇，老實講，想正常返最後都係靠食藥，效果係止唔同，直頭另一個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce218cab1faeff54bab25ee242b3026e07e2925","tid":21694,"uid":29274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T02:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做過幾個網上測驗都話我好大機會有ADHD<br />\n不過我見去搵私家醫生check要成幾千蚊<br />\n想知食完藥效果係咪真係好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果影響唔大就算啦 <br />\n分分鐘食藥嘅附作用重大</blockquote><br />\n有咩副作用？<br />\n記性變差之類？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無ADHD 不過知少少ADHD既野<br />\n只係啲理論野 比樓主參考下<br />\n一般黎講用藥副作用都唔會太嚴重 <br />\n所以好多醫生都會照開藥<br />\n副作用包括影響食慾，失眠，身體有痛感，身體抽搐或者變得情緒化 不過一般黎講都會慢慢改善 或者同醫生講 調節劑量都有可能令副作用減輕<br />\n亦有一說提出食藥會壓抑成長 不過係極少數<br />\n至於食藥係好多情況下都可以減輕過度活躍既情況<br />\n詳細真係要搵醫生傾下"},{"pid":"e8961058c385885f81d7df658fa67139ba49f02d","tid":21694,"uid":46265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做過幾個網上測驗都話我好大機會有ADHD<br />\n不過我見去搵私家醫生check要成幾千蚊<br />\n想知食完藥效果係咪真係好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果影響唔大就算啦 <br />\n分分鐘食藥嘅附作用重大</blockquote><br />\n有咩副作用？<br />\n記性變差之類？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無ADHD 不過知少少ADHD既野<br />\n只係啲理論野 比樓主參考下<br />\n一般黎講用藥副作用都唔會太嚴重 <br />\n所以好多醫生都會照開藥<br />\n副作用包括影響食慾，失眠，身體有痛感，身體抽搐或者變得情緒化 不過一般黎講都會慢慢改善 或者同醫生講 調節劑量都有可能令副作用減輕<br />\n亦有一說提出食藥會壓抑成長 不過係極少數<br />\n至於食藥係好多情況下都可以減輕過度活躍既情況<br />\n詳細真係要搵醫生傾下</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<br />\n我諗我都係搵個醫生睇下"},{"pid":"872bce03d845edf7cade2be093608935d94dba26","tid":21694,"uid":46265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:45:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做過幾個網上測驗都話我好大機會有ADHD<br />\n不過我見去搵私家醫生check要成幾千蚊<br />\n想知食完藥效果係咪真係好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nADHD撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拖左好多年都唔想去睇，老實講，想正常返最後都係靠食藥，效果係止唔同，直頭另一個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食完藥你身邊啲人feel 唔 feel到你唔同左<br />\n有冇讚你"},{"pid":"3f6086e34cf5258e1319fc7ac53a6c5825da7b26","tid":21694,"uid":19385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T00:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/04/123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F04%2F123235_955f8c8bf26edcae9953301a6aa7a815.jpg&h=ffbca39f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做過幾個網上測驗都話我好大機會有ADHD<br />\n不過我見去搵私家醫生check要成幾千蚊<br />\n想知食完藥效果係咪真係好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nADHD撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拖左好多年都唔想去睇，老實講，想正常返最後都係靠食藥，效果係止唔同，直頭另一個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食完藥你身邊啲人feel 唔 feel到你唔同左<br />\n有冇讚你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇，食左藥只會令你可以坐定定做野同思考，記憶力強左，心情好左... 但聽過個老師講，話d學生食左明顯睇到分別。"},{"pid":"a48644040367781e6e7406fe7ae32bfd8064f65c","tid":21694,"uid":5200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T00:13:32.000Z","msg":"係咪家庭醫生先？無時無刻都會走去聽其他人講野<br />\n明明同自己講要專心 都做做下野分左心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}